'''Francisco de Guruceaga Iturriza''' (January 28, 1928 &ndash; February 10, 2012) was the [[Roman Catholic]] bishop of the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of La Guaira]], [[Venezuela]].

Ordained to the priesthood in 1960, de Guruceaga Iturriza became a bishop in 1967 resigning in 2001.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bguritu.html Francisco de Guruceaga Iturriza]</ref>

